{
  "stem": "3771.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It so happened to me that I have to mention to you one particular that happened in the-- in the ghetto of Mlawa, that I watched a horrifying thing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans used to come in in the ghetto [INAUDIBLE] of course for collecting all kind of things, whatever it is-- ransom for this, ransom for that, [INAUDIBLE] came in.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once [INAUDIBLE] I was working there in the street there, and a woman was coming out was holding with a child.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The child must have been maybe a year or something like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] You talk about children-- the children in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They should have been-- the nourishment for the child was so degraded it couldn't grow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could see a child of six, seven years, it would look like four, because this is the time when the body develops.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the German walked over to that woman and stayed there with two others, and I saw the most unbelievable thing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to myself, there must be some human being in them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He opened the thing, and there was a chocolate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He unwrapped the chocolate, and gave the child that chocolate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I was wondering if something is an angel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he gave the piece of chocolate, and he give it to the child, which is licking that piece of chocolate and feeling like this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Suddenly, I noticed he had a pair of gloves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And a pair of gloves was in his belt, like over folded, like-- I remember like today.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He took out the gloves, put on the gloves on his hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Suddenly, he has chain-- changed from a human being to a deadly, vicious animal, in one second.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He grabbed that poor little boy by a foot.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
